1
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:39,217
Mračíš sa.

2
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:57,000
Nad čím premýšľaš?

3
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,500
Ukradol som ti bozk.

4
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,300
Toto bol podľa teba bozk?

5
00:01:57,500 --> 00:02:00,000
Áno.
Moje pery sa dotkli tvojich.

6
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Korn...

7
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,500
Toto bol bozk.

8
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Čo je to s tebou?

9
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,500
Prečo?

10
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,500
Ty si ma pobozkal, ako prvý.

11
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,300
Dobre.

12
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,000
Vzdávam sa.

13
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,500
Som šťastný.

14
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,000
Prepáčte.

15
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,000
Máte túto knihu?

16
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,000
Tú knihu si už niekto požičal.

17
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,500
Nemáte ešte jednu kópiu?

18
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:14,000
Je jedna kópia na fakulte manažmentu.

19
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,000
Môžeš sa ísť pozrieť tam.

20
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
Nemyslím si,
že si ju tam niekto požičal.

21
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:20,000
Ďakujem.

22
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:25,800
<i>Som v knižnici na tvojej fakulte.</i>

23
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:38,000
Už som tu.

24
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:42,000
Nech sa páči.

25
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:47,000
Nezabudnite mi dať neskôr peniaze.

26
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:48,500
Tu máš.

27
00:09:48,500 --> 00:09:49,500
Nezabudnem.

28
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,000
Ozaj, Dean.

29
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
Stretol som Parm-a.

30
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
Ten chalan,
ktorý ma kŕmil svojim dezertom.

31
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:59,000
Je roztomilý.

32
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,500
Videl som ho v knižnici.

33
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,000
Kiežby ma mohol kŕmiť celý deň
a celú noc.

34
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,500
Zjedol by som všetko od neho.

35
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:08,000
Chýbajú mi jeho cukrovinky.

36
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:09,500
Aj mne.

37
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:10,800
Sú také sladké.

38
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
Každý sa do nich zamiluje.

39
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:18,700
Počkať.

40
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:19,500
Kam to ideš?

41
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,500
Idem s tebou.

42
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:22,000
Som hladný.

43
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,000
Pokračujte v učení.

44
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,000
Vrátim sa neskôr.

45
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,000
Počkaj.

46
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,000
Ešte si mi nezaplatil.

47
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,700
Nemám peniaze.

48
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,000
Zase ma okradol?

49
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:39,000
Pravdepodobne.

50
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,000
Späť k práci.

51
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,050
Zase sa tak tváriš.

52
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,000
Snívalo sa ti niečo?

53
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,000
Áno.

54
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:05,000
Môžeš mi o tom povedať.

55
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:07,000
Možno sa budeš cítiť lepšie.

56
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:16,300
Keby si bol na niečo veľmi zvedavý

57
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,500
a odpoveď by bola hneď pred tebou,

58
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:20,500
ale keby si získal svoju odpoveď

59
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,900
veľmi by ťa to ranilo...

60
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,400
Čo by si urobil?

61
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:28,500
Ak viem o určitom riziku,
prečo by som túžil po odpovedi?

62
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:30,500
Nechal by som to tak.

63
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:32,000
Nehľadal by som odpoveď.

64
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,500
Nevyhľadával by som problémy.

65
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:38,000
Lenže ak by som to nechal tak, 

66
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:42,000
bol by som zvedavý po zvyšok svojho života.

67
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,500
Až do mojej smrti.

68
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,000
Niečo sa ťa spýtam.

69
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,400
Keby si sa dozvedel po čom túžiš,
v čom by nastal problém?

70
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,000
Čo by sa tým pokazilo?

71
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,500
Môj vzťah.

72
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:05,000
Mohol by sa mi pokaziť môj vzťah.

73
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:08,000
Možno by sa ale zlepšil.

74
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:09,500
Neviem, ako by to dopadlo.

75
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,500
Čo ak...

76
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:17,000
Čo ak by sa tvoj vzťah naozaj pokazil.

77
00:12:18,300 --> 00:12:20,000
Opustil by si toho človeka?

78
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
Nikdy.

79
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:25,500
Nikdy ho neopustím.

80
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,000
Dobre.

81
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:29,000
Tak nájdi odpoveď na svoju otázku.

82
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:32,000
Povedal si,
že sa možno niečo stane.

83
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,500
Lenže je šanca,
že sa možno nič nestane.

84
00:12:34,500 --> 00:12:36,000
Je to šanca 50:50.

85
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,000
Taktiež...

86
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:39,500
Aj keby sa vyskytol problém,

87
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
si odhodlaný byť s ním navždy.

88
00:12:42,500 --> 00:12:44,500
Prečo sa teda bojíš?

89
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,500
Máš pravdu.

90
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:54,000
Strach vie byť niekedy
najväčšou prekážkou.

91
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:58,000
Možno sa tak bojíš preto,
lebo pre teba Parm veľa znamená.

92
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:01,000
Bojíš sa,
že ho stratíš.

93
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,500
Preto sa bojíš nájsť svoju odpoveď.

94
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,500
Bože.

95
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,700
Vieš povedať aj niečo rozumné.

96
00:13:08,300 --> 00:13:09,300
Debil.

97
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,000
Práve som ti pomohol.

98
00:13:11,700 --> 00:13:13,000
Idem do obchodu.

99
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,000
Choď mi pre knihu.

100
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,000
Potrebujeme ju na tú skúšku.

101
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,000
Dobre.

102
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:19,000
Ozaj.

103
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:21,000
Ver mi.

104
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,300
Tvoj priateľ by sa ťa taktiež nikdy nevzdal.

105
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,120
Maj sa.

